{"title":"eclipse链接Tomcat服务器","slug":"eclipse链接Tomcat服务器","date":"2019-11-01T08:14:18.000Z","updated":"2019-11-10T10:22:19.751Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<h2 id=\"1-打开eclipse-Myelipse\"><a href=\"#1-打开eclipse-Myelipse\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.打开eclipse/Myelipse\"></a>1.打开eclipse/Myelipse</h2><p>打开菜单栏windows/preferences 找到Server里面的Runtime Environments  添加下载好的对应版本的Tomcat服务器 点击next</p>\n<p>如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720191101164615.png\" alt></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/232111442933866.png\" alt></p>\n<p>随后选择Tomcat的所在目录和安装的Java环境</p>\n<p>如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/232112245587963.png\" alt></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-创建jsp项目\"><a href=\"#2-创建jsp项目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.创建jsp项目\"></a>2.创建jsp项目</h2><p>点击File —&gt;new 找到里面的Dynamic Web Project 创建项目 </p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/222.png\" alt></p>\n<p>点击下方Finish</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-创建jsp文件\"><a href=\"#3-创建jsp文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.创建jsp文件\"></a>3.创建jsp文件</h2><p>此时jsp项目已经生成 现在只需在WebContent下新建JSP文件（注意 必须在WebContent此目录下创建 千万别选成META-INF或WEB-INF了 会报错）</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720191101165734.png\" alt=\"1572598667893\"></p>\n<p>在body中写入 Hello world 运行一下 就可以在网页中显示啦</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720191101170501.png\" alt></p>\n<p>以后就可以用eclipse写网页了 </p>\n<p>（jsp的弊端：前后端不能实现真正分离 高耦合 低效率）</p>\n","thumbnail":"/img/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/dd.jpg","primarycolor":"blueGrey","accentcolor":"blueGrey","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"一giao我哩giao","path":"api/tags/一giao我哩giao.json"}]}